The common factor of 3 in the numerator and the common factor of 3 in the denominator will cancel: \[
\frac{3^4+3^2}{3^3-3}=\frac{3(3^3+3^1)}{3(3^2-1)}=\frac{3^3+3^1}{3^2-1}
